    role: str
    content: str
    images: list[str] = field(default_factory=list)
    audios: list[str] = field(default_factory=list)  # 추가
```
`stream_generate(audio=[...])` 호출 추가. mlx-vlm 0.4.4는 audio kwarg 지원 (Phi-4-multimodal).

**사이드카 `api/openai.py`**:
```python
class OpenAIAudioBody(BaseModel):
    data: str  # base64 or data URL
    format: Literal["mp3", "wav", "flac", "m4a"]

class OpenAIAudioPart(BaseModel):
    type: Literal["input_audio"]
    input_audio: OpenAIAudioBody

OpenAIContentPart = OpenAITextPart | OpenAIImagePart | OpenAIAudioPart
```

